01:02:54.130 --> 01:02:56.190
and are really just
looking for that research

01:02:56.190 --> 01:02:58.730
to be sort of distilled
down, so as much as we

01:02:58.730 --> 01:03:00.350
can get that information out.

01:03:00.350 --> 01:03:02.970
So what we're finding is
that John and Julie Gottman,

01:03:02.970 --> 01:03:04.390
they hold these
couples workshops.

01:03:04.390 --> 01:03:06.490
And people fly in from
